OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA clear and
OL,6,Fdry night to start. Low cloud moving
OL,7,Finto the west during the early hours
OL,8,Fwhich could bring a spot of rain.
OL,9,FStaying very mild.
OL,10,
OL,11,CFriday:FLow cloud in the west will
OL,12,Flift through the morning, leaving a
OL,13,Fdry and bright day for most, with warm
OL,14,Fhazy sunshine. Temperatures continue
OL,15,Fto rise above the May average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
