OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FVery
OL,6,Fwarm over the Bank Holiday weekend
OL,7,Fwith plenty of sunshine and light
OL,8,Fwinds. Any early morning cloud should
OL,9,Fburn back to the coasts through the
OL,10,Fmorning each day.
